I was very disappointed with their service. Never got the chance to taste the food. I went to the store ordered by pointing to the menu pics of a #5 Whiting sandwich and a #6 Italian cheese burger and said no fries or soda. (Why they would call a cheeseburger with american cheese Italian idk). I told one of the young women working there with no hairnet  that I wanted the cheeseburger with lettuce tomato and ketcup on the side . I waited in the non air condition for a good while, when presented with my order I received a cheeseburger with fries in the sandwhich. Then I was told that that's how the pic on the menu was and it's not. The fish sandwich was supposed to be on a hero I was given one on a small bun. When I complained , the woman took the order back but made no real response. I thought about it for a minute and decided to leave. She stopped me said fish was ready. So,  I said ok just give me the fish, forget the cheeseburger. She handed me a bag with 2 pieces of fish in it. I refused to pay or take the order.  She told me never to come back. No loss for me, I will gladly never enter 98k again!!
